      • fadeIn

        public Title.Builder fadeIn(@Nullable
                            Integer fadeIn)
        Sets the duration in ticks of the fade in effect of the title. Once this period of time is over the title will stay for the amount of time specified in stay(Integer).

        The default value for Vanilla is 20 (1 second).

        Parameters:
        fadeIn - The amount of ticks (1/20 second) for the fade in effect, or null to reset
        Returns:
        This title builder

      • stay

        public Title.Builder stay(@Nullable
                          Integer stay)
        Sets the duration in ticks how long the title should stay on the screen. Once this period of time is over the title will fade out using the duration specified in fadeOut(Integer).

        The default value for Vanilla is 60 (3 seconds).

        Parameters:
        stay - The amount of ticks (1/20 second) to stay, or null to reset
        Returns:
        This title builder
        See Also:
        Title.getStay()
